{"tid":1440414,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"偽黃屍店舖 巴絲別上檔","createTime":"2019-08-10T12:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T13:41:06.000Z","uid":121029,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"876a9541369a4332049e54f47d82163c9c9654ab","tid":1440414,"uid":121029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"[代post ]<br />\n<br />\n本來認為只係抽水POST啦<br />\n其實17年就已經出左通告話CCTV只會比警察睇<br />\n而會裝既原因只係因為想保障店方, 例如好似偷竊依類<br />\n<br />\n但店方星期二就改左個通告話只要有半數老闆同意就可以交片<br />\n而聽聞老闆係兩夫妻, 即係一個人同意就可以交片??<br />\n而睇番圖呢, 一入門口就已經有CCTV<br />\n入左門口就影到, 之後只要老闆其中一人鐘意就比咩人都得<br />\n<br />\n點解店方唔係澄清個POST係舊, 而係改POST呢?<br />\n<br />\n藍屍可恥, 偽黃屍更可恥<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HczEUjX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHczEUjX.jpg&h=edb699f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TRD6zjX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTRD6zjX.jpg&h=5f9089ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1eOBWyi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1eOBWyi.jpg&h=7404a3d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ns9Q0Z0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNs9Q0Z0.jpg&h=e250123f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2c7e94d3f82f447d077b8e462b8b5d9dc299d2b","tid":1440414,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}